{
    "ai-tha-ap532:0.1_0": "Therāpadāna",
    "ai-tha-ap532:0.2_0": "Tiṇadāyakavagga",
    "ai-tha-ap532:0.3_0": "10. Sugandhattheraapadāna",
    "ai-tha-ap532:1.1_0": "“My dear barber,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:1.2_0": "the great bonds of Brahmā;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:1.3_0": "Kassapa,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:1.4_0": "‘Calmness has arisen in you,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:2.1_0": "One who is accomplished in views,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:2.2_0": "thirty-two marks of Bārāṇasī.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:2.3_0": "surrounded by currents",
    "ai-tha-ap532:2.4_0": "caught in the net of rain.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:3.1_0": "like the moon in the waning on the moon,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:3.2_0": "like the sun shining in the light.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:3.3_0": "like a thunder cloud,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:3.4_0": "make the ocean, though all the gods.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:4.1_0": "Riches lazy",
    "ai-tha-ap532:4.2_0": "Himalaya besides, immersion.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:4.3_0": "like a monkey in wisdom.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:4.4_0": "As the Saṅgha’s tireless is not,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:5.1_0": "always great hero,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:5.2_0": "self-assured in the assemblies.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:5.3_0": "truthfully—",
    "ai-tha-ap532:5.4_0": "ends of the people.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:6.1_0": "Then in Bārāṇasī, at that time the Fortunate One was living near Bārāṇasī,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:6.2_0": "But the son of a prominent merchant,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:6.3_0": "I’m the one who looks after immeasurable wealth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:6.4_0": "it was abundant food and drink.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:7.1_0": "I wandered around and entering a dwelling.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:7.2_0": "trapped in the deer—",
    "ai-tha-ap532:7.3_0": "I saw the stainless Buddha",
    "ai-tha-ap532:7.4_0": "he’s teaching the deathless state.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:8.1_0": "they’ve reached the goal",
    "ai-tha-ap532:8.2_0": "The hero, the hero,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:8.3_0": "stuck up, withered swords,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:8.4_0": "he asked for the benefit of the great crowd.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:9.1_0": "Having seen (that), the Lord of the Gods",
    "ai-tha-ap532:9.2_0": "crushing the sweet,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:9.3_0": "After giving up wealth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:9.4_0": "I went forth to homelessness.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:10.1_0": "so I went forth.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:10.2_0": "after no long time, learned much of the teaching,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:10.3_0": "I was a Dhamma speaker.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:10.4_0": "the eloquence of meaning",
    "ai-tha-ap532:11.1_0": "I am his equal,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:11.2_0": "on account of his mind again and again his (himself) is unaffected.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:11.3_0": "golden colored,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:11.4_0": "praiseworthy.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:12.1_0": "‘That’s a Buddha, with defilements ended,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:12.2_0": "untroubled, with doubts cut off.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:12.3_0": "he has attained the ending of all deeds.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:12.4_0": "freed with the end of craving.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:13.1_0": "That Blessed One is the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:13.2_0": "he is the supreme lion,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:13.3_0": "in all the world with its gods,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:13.4_0": "reached the spiritual path.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:14.1_0": "tamer and tamed,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:14.2_0": "Also the hermits have been agreed upon,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:14.3_0": "Extinguishment is the unattached,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:14.4_0": "The people bring great crowds,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:15.1_0": "Rohitassa and Rohiṇī",
    "ai-tha-ap532:15.2_0": "his wisdom is like a lion,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:15.3_0": "victorious, victor,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:15.4_0": "uneducated,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:16.1_0": "An imperturbable, tamed,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:16.2_0": "free of delusion, without confusion.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:16.3_0": "like a bull elephant,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:16.4_0": "such a wide open,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:17.1_0": "dispassion, so Brahmā,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:17.2_0": "Speaker is the nation,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:17.3_0": "shameless, poisonous,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:17.4_0": "alert and irreversible.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:18.1_0": "a true ascetic, not a brahmin.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:18.2_0": "a trainer, an arrow,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:18.3_0": "The wise one who is very learned,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:18.4_0": "Saged, unshakable,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:19.1_0": "Both are caught and thieves,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:19.2_0": "what leads out of compassion.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:19.3_0": "if breakage and foster;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:19.4_0": "They’ve cut off the stream,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:20.1_0": "shameless, poisonous,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:20.2_0": "stilled and free of indecision,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:20.3_0": "one who is lustful, unfrettering,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:20.4_0": "conduct themselves well.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:21.1_0": "they bride the grounds,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:21.2_0": "Accomplishments,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:21.3_0": "while the wicked are types of wickedness,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:21.4_0": "keen and prudent,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:22.1_0": "equal to oneself.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:22.2_0": "sympathy, and sympathy,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:22.3_0": "deliberate lies,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:22.4_0": "seventh of the sages.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:23.1_0": "free of doubt, free of doubt,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:23.2_0": "it’s immeasurable,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:23.3_0": "avoiding all the path of crossing.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:23.4_0": "you’ll realize the truth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:24.1_0": "Seventh in that place,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:24.2_0": "confidence in the deathless,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:24.3_0": "Therefore the Buddha and the Dhamma,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:24.4_0": "who are faithful in the Saṅgha,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:25.1_0": "thus practise,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:25.2_0": "supremely blessed himself.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:25.3_0": "praised by the assembly.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:25.4_0": "talk on Dhamma,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:26.1_0": "When I fall from there,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:26.2_0": "having given up pleasure and happiness,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:26.3_0": "passing away from there and rebirth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:26.4_0": "I’m born in a charnel ground,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:27.1_0": "carrionfies and mouth:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:27.2_0": "like the fragrant “Give me a little”,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:27.3_0": "hanging to sweat,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:27.4_0": "He washed all smells;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:28.1_0": "like a fragrant mouth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:28.2_0": "Padumavatī was adorned with watersumed.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:28.3_0": "if he makes it quiver;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:28.4_0": "just as I had a body",
    "ai-tha-ap532:29.1_0": "Virtuous in every way,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:29.2_0": "which you say is the ultimate fruit.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:29.3_0": "May all beings arise",
    "ai-tha-ap532:29.4_0": "I will listen to you,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:30.1_0": "attained to the Buddha and worshipped him.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:30.2_0": "I have no equal or hope",
    "ai-tha-ap532:30.3_0": "May I be happy!",
    "ai-tha-ap532:30.4_0": "The Saṅgha, the Saṅgha:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:31.1_0": "the one who had no possessions",
    "ai-tha-ap532:31.2_0": "beholds to see him,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:31.3_0": "he’s behaved and undefeated.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:31.4_0": "free of hate.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:32.1_0": "you’ll attain quenching.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:32.2_0": "I gained the Buddha.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:32.3_0": "it is the same for them to do it.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:32.4_0": "listen to this, for it is the truth.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:33.1_0": "peacefully, Yasa,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:33.2_0": "by bowing down to the sea.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:33.3_0": "Herein, the meaning there is this:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:33.4_0": "I am the one who sits by that,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:34.1_0": "pursuing the Buddha’s teaching.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:34.2_0": "the truth of the unconditioned,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:34.3_0": "happiness, and embracing happiness,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:34.4_0": "from there to beings,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:35.1_0": "speaking kindly to the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:35.2_0": "the calm of the Buddha:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:35.3_0": "who sleeps with others:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:35.4_0": "a person would build (them).",
    "ai-tha-ap532:36.1_0": "They were crowded by ascetics of other religions,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:36.2_0": "Mastered by the sectarians,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:36.3_0": "Victors, speaking kindly.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:36.4_0": "you were not burnt by fire.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:37.1_0": "Doing what you need?",
    "ai-tha-ap532:37.2_0": "speaking of the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:37.3_0": "with corruption, fearful;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:37.4_0": "At that time I was like a father,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:38.1_0": "likewise spend the rainy season.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:38.2_0": "with peaceful words and poison.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:38.3_0": "the Holy One or the place where I am",
    "ai-tha-ap532:38.4_0": "the eloquence of meaning",
    "ai-tha-ap532:39.1_0": "have fed the fool with wisdom.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:39.2_0": "a great sage, destroyer of fame,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:39.3_0": "Your teaching has been correctly memorized by you.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:39.4_0": "I wouldn’t be a layperson.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:40.1_0": "to the Buddha’s praise,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:40.2_0": "defilements are defiled.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:40.3_0": "I’m free from defilements,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:40.4_0": "the winds of his deeds,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:41.1_0": "grows old to growth,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:41.2_0": "Recollection of the Buddha.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:41.3_0": "Hence I’m wise,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:41.4_0": "you’re considered to bear;",
    "ai-tha-ap532:42.1_0": "With the utter ending of all defilements,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:42.2_0": "Thirty—",
    "ai-tha-ap532:42.3_0": "by not grasping, like aassing.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:42.4_0": "I’ll attain quenched.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:43.1_0": "in this place",
    "ai-tha-ap532:43.2_0": "A peaceful one,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:43.3_0": "I’m not aware of any living being",
    "ai-tha-ap532:43.4_0": "is the color of the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:44.1_0": "corrupted by defilements,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:44.2_0": "... “I’ll sleep ...”",
    "ai-tha-ap532:44.3_0": "and live without defilements.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:45.1_0": "It was so welcome for me",
    "ai-tha-ap532:45.2_0": "... “I’ll sleep ...”",
    "ai-tha-ap532:45.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:46.1_0": "the four analytical knowledges,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:46.2_0": "... “I’ll sleep ...”",
    "ai-tha-ap532:46.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "ai-tha-ap532:47.1_0": "That is how these verses were recited by the senior venerable Sumdha.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:48.1_0": "having endless perfumes made of timberges.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:49.1_0": "the tip of grass is equal to the youthful.",
    "ai-tha-ap532:50.1_0": "This is the summary:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:51.1_0": "A grass torch and arrows,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:51.2_0": "to rough grace",
    "ai-tha-ap532:51.3_0": "well-being and lady,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:51.4_0": "likewise and so on,",
    "ai-tha-ap532:52.1_0": "I stepped in the Awakening story:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:52.2_0": "fragrant and ten:",
    "ai-tha-ap532:52.3_0": "Though the hundred spears",
    "ai-tha-ap532:52.4_0": "and picked up (follows) in every way,"
}